# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# React Perf Profiler — Landing page environment variables
# Copy this file to landing/.env and fill in the values.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Email capture (choose ONE option) ───────────────────────────

# Option A: Formspree (free tier, no server required)
# 1. Create a form at https://formspree.io
# 2. Copy the form ID (last segment of your form URL)
# VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=xxxxxxxx

# Option B: Custom REST endpoint (POST { email, source })
# VITE_EMAIL_ENDPOINT=https://your-api.example.com/subscribe

# ── Analytics ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Plausible Analytics — privacy-preserving, no cookies required.
# 1. Create a site at https://plausible.io (free for open-source)
# 2. Set this to your GitHub Pages domain, e.g. rejisterjack.github.io
# 3. Uncomment the <script> tag in landing/index.html
# VITE_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN=rejisterjack.github.io
